Titolo: Tiger Road

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Tiger Road (Japanese: 虎への道, Hepburn: Tora e no Michi) is a side-scrolling platform game originally released in 1987 as a coin-operated arcade game.
Home computer versions were released in Europe by U.S. Gold for the Amiga, Amstrad CPC, Atari ST, Commodore 64, DOS and ZX Spectrum. An alternate version for the Commodore 64 was released in the  United States by Capcom who also published an Amiga 500 port of the game in that region.
A remade version for the PC Engine/TurboGrafx 16 was released in 1990 in Japan and North America.
The original arcade game is included in Capcom Classics Collection Vol. 2 for the PlayStation 2 and Xbox.

